short_description: Lesbian Love in the GDR: Six very different women talk about their lives and loves in real socialism. A balancing act between cold waters and dry land. Six lives, before and after the Fall of the Berlin Wall.
also_known_as: ['Uferfrauen: Lesbian Life and Love in the GDR']
